cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for producing word representations. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of ensemble methods, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper uses word analogy tasks, which is a common evaluation metric in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of different datasets, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper discusses achieving state-of-the-art performance, which is a common goal in neural networks (cs.NE).
